Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行中的妈妈突然回到家中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却得知她正在做一份「邪神猎人」的零工
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与我相撞的这孩子说自己正在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.67,0:00:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住址呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有户主的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.25,0:00:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这家人姓八坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找的人的名字叫什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  八坂赖子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在寻找的人正是我妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.08,0:00:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但话说回来  为什么你爸爸会找我妈妈有事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没问详细的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.62,0:01:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年和莲太看起来很般配
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子就交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年你就培育新的爱苗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我…慢着！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.82,0:01:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻臂弯中的位置永远都是属于我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.82,0:01:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这理由很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.20,0:01:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  妨碍别人恋情的家伙会被乌尔塔尔的猫抓哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你才是吧  把莲太老弟硬配对给真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想我会把你当做备胎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.10,0:01:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们闹够了没
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}就算少年不和莲太在一起  他也应该与地球人交往
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.75,0:01:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你好烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.01,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…般配吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTA-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～我以个人经验研究了一下真寻妈妈和莲太爸爸的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.05,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么想他们都不可能有关联吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我即将说的一切都只不过是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为莲太爸爸和真寻妈妈原先是夫妇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fs20\shad0\1c000000\3c99FEF6}巧克力烟斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.38,0:03:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时他们生下了真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人分手之后  莲太老弟也诞生了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后莲太爸爸回忆起从前的快乐时光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉自己无论如何都无法忘记真寻妈妈  所以想再见她一面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就让莲太老弟去寻妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.97,0:03:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hell Missionaries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  真寻是我哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了  奈亚子讲的话基本上都是胡说八道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻如果是哥哥  还真有点不愿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.29,0:04:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  毕竟我也不是那么优秀的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.87,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不是…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻如果是哥哥的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就不能成为恋人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙没救了  得赶快做点什么才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立了立了  Flag立起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3c7A2BE3\shad0\fscx75\bord6}伟大的X的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:41.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(250,65)\1c7A2BE3\3cFFFFFF\shad0\fscx75}伟大的X的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这里就是我家了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是漂亮的房子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}（那就是环保！！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}（地球马上就要撑不住了）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:04:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位就是真寻的妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.05,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.99,0:05:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小寻的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我叫莲太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要从朋友开始做起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.26,0:05:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真乖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您万万不可被这可爱的外表给骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:17.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我们一样也是不折不扣的邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲太老弟  稍微过来下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.57,0:05:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.44,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看中真寻的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾  又没规定先到先得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是妹子更好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  老待外面也不是个事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.64,0:05:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先进屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以受到招待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.65,0:05:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻的房间…好紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.08,0:05:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲太飘飘然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这些  你还有事找妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.18,0:06:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.86,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部不许动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是何方神圣！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是八坂赖子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈斯塔  你们也盯上这位女士了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会知道我的名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装什么傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把这位女士交给你们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:49.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为胜利的一方是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.70,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.09,0:06:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…请问找我有什么事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您还没明白自己的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.59,0:07:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将您笼络到的阵营  甚至能够掌握宇宙霸权
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然有时会去打工  当当邪神猎人什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.12,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但完全不是什么大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.39,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授和研究会里其他的前辈比我优秀多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说值得尊敬的人的话  应该是爸爸了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要说的话  小寻也…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.95,0:07:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是准备装傻吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别相信那种家伙说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.01,0:07:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈  到底怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我不去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是为了救我们而不得不牺牲自己吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.91,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下连本人都同意了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.53,0:07:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有你们出场的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了奈亚子  把妈妈救回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:07:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes My Lord！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样  女王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.95,0:08:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我让开  克子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你挡着我杀不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打的什么算盘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦  最爱的真寻将我公主抱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是说蠢话的时候么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.78,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.64,0:08:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来  克子居然会倒戈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胜利的将会是我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.26,0:09:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不会让你们跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.58,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办…怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请冷静下来  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这让人怎么冷静啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.77,0:09:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  其实大部分问题都可以用空手道来解决
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.51,0:09:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好烫好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己是女子高中生侦探吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.27,0:09:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是莲太把那个消除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他姑且是个风之邪神
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「姑且」是多余的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.73,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊  莲太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.36,0:10:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.25,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很努力不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.04,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活着真好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是做这种事的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点去救妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.96,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不能就这样放着不管
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们来商量对策吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on baby
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.33,0:10:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是自己家最舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茶真好喝～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是真寻的家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}绿茶果然还是要喝玉露茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  茶梗立起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.87,0:10:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兆头好兆头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天肯定会有好事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.67,0:11:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.32,0:11:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(263,323)\fs20}混沌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.30,0:11:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然在少女水嫩嫩的肌肤上…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了  为什么还在悠闲地喝茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说「商量对策」的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.92,0:11:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}我已经联系行星保护机构的上司  现在正帮我们探明克子的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.97,0:11:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.40,0:11:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  莲太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不还在那边的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是真寻的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.37,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  莲太老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自作主张地在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.28,0:11:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想问问爸爸到底是什么事  所以打了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:12:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可他似乎因为工作太忙了  没说成
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.97,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人说过这话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.57,0:12:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下就有可能手握宇宙的霸权了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.97,0:12:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底  母亲大人有什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.46,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.57,0:12:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  说不定就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釨元素！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在补充釨元素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那只是妈妈乱说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在别人眼里肯定比托马森还没用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：托马森：指棒球运动员Gary Thomasson\N他曾经创造过一年被三振132次的纪录
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.92,0:12:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一是厉害得不得了的啥未知元素怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定是能颠覆宇宙的强大能量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  釨元素是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.37,0:12:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻的母亲大人通过和真寻碰触
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能产生的迷之营养素
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样  抱着真寻就能产生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.76,0:13:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  还能这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  产生出来的不是迷之营养素  是个孩子也成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  你给我适可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能不能也生产出真寻元素呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:16.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上司吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.92,0:13:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢货  克子已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.64,0:13:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太得意忘形了  课长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要扣我的有薪假期
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  你查到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克子一事就交予我处理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.68,0:13:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也应该是事出有因
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在酿成惨剧之前  我会负责…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这说那的  关键时刻还是会挺克子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.63,0:13:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉克子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果  妈妈和克子在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是在宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.63,0:13:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  在地球
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南纬47.9度  西经126.43度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报坐标我听不懂啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  正是拉莱耶乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.94,0:14:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这次事件的主谋并非犯罪组织
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有克苏鲁株式会社的内部人员才能进入下沉了的拉莱耶乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  绑架犯是那里的员工吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  母亲大人是自愿同行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.09,0:14:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能当做绑架事件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许妈妈是自愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.45,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算说我任性也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无论如何也想带回妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.11,0:14:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你会这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.29,0:14:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想为真寻尽一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了  莲太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.73,0:15:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然决定了  就立马出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.87,0:15:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.67,0:15:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得上次我们去拉莱耶的时候是骑大衮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大衮效忠于克苏鲁公司  这次用不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心  瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.75,0:15:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅弗连卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就决定是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的爱车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水陆两用的特殊车辆  涅弗连卡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陆地上无论多么恶劣的路况它也能轻松行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.21,0:15:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水上自不用说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在海底也能跑得了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.85,0:15:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样？帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.14,0:15:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们去拉莱耶的时候为啥不坐这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不懂行啊  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事初期就入手船只的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动范围不就太广了么  很为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中期坐船终章飞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是常识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最恨别人有本事揣着不使
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.07,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.68,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.32,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞轮  启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量120%
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.78,0:16:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动档啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,15)\fs14\shad0\1c000000\3cFFFFFF\bord3}普通车也只能开自动档
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算开自动档我也能攻略大峡谷和火焰跑道！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好多鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.31,0:16:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深潜者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来不会让我们轻易接近拉莱耶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.22,0:16:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们来了  奈亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.48,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我们逃得掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一会  还有一会量就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.04,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥量？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算存够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.04,0:17:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上魂和气合的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.18,0:17:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一发地图炮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅弗连卡搭载的无限鱼雷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么心狠手辣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有哪有  我有留情的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于我并没有克苏鲁那边参与犯罪的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我还是乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.05,0:17:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.00,0:17:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  我坐车很容易晕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.51,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你  晕车药
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这啥歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入场曲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dagon-a My House
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BOSS终于要登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.29,0:18:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有药  没水冲服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿特拉克·纳茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事  这里怎么会有岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这是大衮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  奈亚子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.60,0:18:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量也空了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么甩掉它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下车  我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈亚子  开稳点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就到拉莱耶了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧  能看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的  总算能平安到达呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.80,0:18:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了海德拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  真寻  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.12,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲太吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子我们还是到达了拉莱耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  我居然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.76,0:19:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是拜它所赐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.10,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被这个救了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.48,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像呛到水了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.03,0:19:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里后就没呼吸过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就给你做了人工呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然看起来像女生  但莲太是男人啊  是男人啊男人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.48,0:20:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这绝对不算数  不算数嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的理论武装能行得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.97,0:20:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行得通  没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.79,0:20:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  奈亚子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你担心奈亚子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  总归有点担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻  你听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一见钟情是存在的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜…喜欢真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.19,0:20:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你合体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  莲太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都是男人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.22,0:20:44.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是我喜欢上的人  碰巧也是个男人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见面我撞上你  被你拉起来时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你温暖的手掌触碰到的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就有感觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.54,0:20:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  有这么一个说法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界的一切以两千五百万年为周期运作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  过了这么久后  一切的一切都会和现在完全一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.07,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说  如果过了两千五百万年后  你这份心意尚未改变的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.75,0:21:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时我会欣然接纳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.86,0:21:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拉钩钩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾勾手指头
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人就喝上一千杯哈利湖的水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20}注：哈利与日文中的针同音  哈利湖为哈斯塔栖身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  奈亚子的气味从那边传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.47,0:21:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气味？你凭气味就能知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有克子的气味  她似乎和奈亚子在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  快走吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为担心我飞奔而来  你太体贴了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是无奈啊  剧情安排啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.26,0:23:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教师生涯25年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.44,0:23:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是教师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.28,0:23:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真寻你总算害羞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.38,0:23:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没害羞好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话「市场里的战争」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.19,0:23:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.09,0:23:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？合体机器人的段子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  被和谐了


